<s> an attempted refinement.. Data Model (WC): The way that information is organised.  </s>
<s> For example, a database might contain information about a customer, classified as an address, a name, a birthdate, and a picture.  </s>
<s> A web page might contain a list of lists, where each sub-list contains (in order) a family name, an initial, a street, a city, and a URI.  </s>
